<li>Jardim, Anne. <i>The First Henry Ford: A Study in Personality and Business Leadership</i> Massachusetts Inst. of Technology Press 1970.</li>
<li>Lacey, Robert. <i>Ford: The Men and the Machine</i> Little, Brown, 1986. popular biography</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLewis1976">Lewis, David I. (1976). <i>The Public Image of Henry Ford: An American Folk Hero and His Company</i>. Wayne State University Press.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Public+Image+of+Henry+Ford%3A+An+American+Folk+Hero+and+His+Company&amp;rft.aulast=Lewis&amp;rft.aufirst=David+I.&amp;rft.au=Lewis%2C+David+I.&amp;rft.date=1976&amp;rft.pub=Wayne+State+University+Press&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Henry_Ford"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
