<li>Lee, Albert; <i>Henry Ford and the Jews</i>; Rowman &amp; Littlefield Publishers, Inc., 1980; <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0812827015" class="internal">ISBN 0-8128-2701-5</a></li>
